x264_encode
===========

My video x264 mkv encoding script.
This script is acting as a wrapper to mencoder/x264 and mkvmerge and
encodes more or less everything to a mkv file with h264 video and mp3 audio.

Usage:
./x264_encode.py [options] <file> : Encode <file> with options.
./x264_encode.py -f <file> : Encode files defined in <file>

Options:
-v <value> : Videobitrate will be set to <value>. Default 5000.
-s X:Y : Scale video to X:Y.
-l <language> : Sets language to <language>. Use like de or en here.
